data.description: Positioned alongside neighboring properties already aligning with the City's comprehensive plan, this unique parcel holds the promise of transformation. With the city of Nampa's approval, envision crafting 3 to 4 Townhome sites, each thoughtfully designed to blend seamlessly into the fabric of the community. Adding to the allure is a 1680 ft² one-story residential home on the property, presenting many possibilities. Imagine converting it into dynamic commercial offices, establishing it as a lucrative rental property, or preserving its residential charm. The choice is yours, offering flexibility that caters to various investment objectives. This property not only stands as a testament to growth but also as a canvas for innovation. Embrace the opportunity to shape the landscape of this evolving neighborhood, aligning with the city's vision for thoughtful and dynamic development. Seize the chance to be part of something transformative. A real estate endeavor poised for success in the flourishing City of Nampa.
